'''Kristanvponn''' zaun asa ek ''monotheistic'' dhorm, mhonnge ekuch devan visvas thevpi, ani ho dhorm [[Jezu|Jezu Kristache]] jivitacher adarlelem asa. Kristanvponn sonvsaracho soglleantlo vhoddlo dhorm zache 2.4 billion vangddi asat, zanka Kristanv mhonntat. Kristanv mantat ki Jezu zaun asa Devacho Put, akho deivik ani akho munis, ani to soglea monxeancho sodvonndar mhonn, zachem vixim pornem koraran boroilelem aslem.

Kristanv mantat ki Jezun koxtt sosle, to melo, taka nikipilo, ani to mornantlo punorjivont zalo, techer aplea patkanche bhogsonne mellche pasot visvas thevteleank sasnachem jivit diunche khatir.

Kristanvponnache tin vhoddle fantte zaun asat [[Katolik firgoz]], Orthodox firgoz, ani Protestant. Katolik ani Orthodox firgoz 11ve xekdeant vegle zalet, Protestant 16ve xekdean ostitvant ailem.

